In Scala 2.11, you can use "typeOf".
In Scala 2.10, use "manifest" instead of "typeOf".

Example:
- Code for Scala 2.11: https://github.com/xitrum-framework/xitrum/blob/master/src/main/scala-2.11/xitrum/scope/request/ParamAccess.scala
- Equivalent code for Scala 2.10: https://github.com/xitrum-framework/xitrum/blob/master/src/main/scala-2.10/xitrum/scope/request/ParamAccess.scala
